{"tid":1027650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少爺占商台新春團拜疑爆粗  森美急救亡打圓場","createTime":"2019-02-19T02:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T04:01:07.000Z","uid":9573,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf7e32bed68f922b3b0ad42166e008d476826cd","tid":1027650,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:55:06.000Z","msg":"森美、少爺占、當奴、林海峰及葛民輝等昨日齊集商台新春團拜，眾主持以猜燈謎方式介紹節目，當少爺占讀出謎面「廣播道名校」後，望向當奴說：「咁X難估？」森美即為少爺占打圓場笑說：「你嚟緊係想爆騷，唔係爆粗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190219/large/19ec3p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190219%2Flarge%2F19ec3p8.jpg&h=20f78f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商台今年推動運動，首項計劃是邀請香港短跑紀錄保持者親授陳志雲正確跑姿，一改他在08奥運傳火炬時，接梁振英棒後的「師奶跑」步姿。"},{"pid":"9b2246e6d905c226c417cc48d85c5d7b0bf568bd","tid":1027650,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c0ee9260840df7c50833cb862d532cafd4038a","tid":1027650,"uid":220431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"香港短跑紀錄保持者親授陳志雲正確跑姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4074a15440a221457ca29ac18cda0dda21618a89","tid":1027650,"uid":159333,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:36:42.000Z","msg":"睇左幾次都睇成 香港短跑紀錄保持者陳志雲親授正確跑姿"},{"pid":"b21b9686d1d1e13a5c1f5e41d8264fb1e746fb48","tid":1027650,"uid":36372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"又話不和"},{"pid":"ccf773383f46d2b0d808e6882daf18142ad01938","tid":1027650,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}